.compact-name {
  font-weight: 600;
  line-height: 1.15;
  font-size: clamp(0.56rem, 1.1vw, 0.76rem);
  word-break: break-word;
  overflow-wrap: anywhere;
  display: -webkit-box;
  -webkit-line-clamp: 2;
  -webkit-box-orient: vertical;
  overflow: hidden;
}
.compact-cell {
  padding: 8px 4px;
}
```

